jsonld_description:
Introducing our third drop of our new format Limited Editions! Walter White Bx1 isn’t our first backcross; with our Artisanals line we put in the work and take things to a level that not many others do. As with our Livers BX1 project which took 12 generations of breeding to get to the point of release; our Walter White BX1 has been a labour of love, beginning the second outcross to our cut of Krome’s ‘The White’ in 2018. Whilst bringing out Walter White BX1 to F5, we set aside a number of choice pollen donors to match with some epic females from across the Mephisto Genetics catalogue. As these are true F1 Limited Editions, they are untested aside from our usual rigorous germination and quality control tests. Available only in packs of 5 seeds. 
Short and stocky, expect a heavy indica hybrid with a flavour profile to die for and frost levels up the wazoo.

jsonld_description:
Willy's Gum
Old School Mango Haze x HubbaBubbaHaze15/85
Bubblegum, mango and that classic haze goodness. Sweet on the nose and the inhale, she’s more complex than the name might give her credit for. Expect a bigger girl that might take some taming, but the work will be more than worth it in the end.

jsonld_description: All Illuminauto strains are untested, aside from our usual germination and general quality control tests. These seeds are listed more cheaply than our usual catalogue items, as we use these lines as a testbed to find the best fire to add to our catalogue for longer-term use.Released as part of our June 2023 Illuminautos Drop

jsonld_description:
Wedding Doves
Mephisto's Wedding x Ravenberry
Mephisto's Wedding and Ravenberry's union results in Wedding Doves. This strain is like a matrimonial celebration, bursting with love, sweet berry flavours, and a hint of festive spice.

jsonld_description: You are cordially invited to witness the union of our beautiful farm friends Marley and Pepper! Our first strain to be bred outside of our little farmstead in España, and instead in our new home in the US by Nico in NorCal. Using Seed Junky’s legendary Wedding Cake cut crossed to Double Grape to make our F1 selections and then carrying them over the threshold with a particularly special ‘Mitch’s Pick’ selection of our ever-popular Creme de la Chem, we have created what we can proudly say is the best Wedding Cake auto a grower can find.
